  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Great Divide Lodge is an exciting addition to our Lake Louise programme this year, with a truly exceptional array of added value offers, with meals and drinks, your lift-pass and equipment rental all included in the cost of your holiday!</p>
<p><strong>Location:</strong> The lodge is situated just inside the British Columbia border on the famously scenic Kicking Horse Pass. The superb Lake Louise ski area is just 10 minutes away using the free ski bus and you can also have an away day skiing in the Kicking Horse area (bookable locally through our resort representative).</p>]]></description>
